{"tid":2069520,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"火星異警","createTime":"2020-06-18T12:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T12:39:56.000Z","uid":340729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0c56d2ab6d94418a4d06e537783716ceccc6c6","tid":2069520,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"元朗國，香港特別行政區其一郊區。<br />\n本來的平均氣溫華氐64度，大氣壓０.721氣壓，為了把這和平的郊區改變成人類可以居住。<br />\n二十一世紀中葉，二種生物先於人類被送到了火星，其中一種是特殊的鄉黑，而另一種是有強大繁殖能力，生命力強大的昆蟲，警甴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1223cock.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1223cock.png&h=e74b46bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">樓主回應：係，真係好強大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n利申：樓主岩岩睇完第一集，幾好睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反應好又得閒整個完整版先。"}]}